# 实时数据监控接口测试文件
# 使用 VS Code 的 REST Client 插件或 IntelliJ IDEA 的 HTTP Client 运行

### 1. 测试获取仪表列表
GET http://localhost:8080/jeecg-boot/energy/realtime/test/testGetModules
Accept: application/json

### 2. 测试获取参数配置
GET http://localhost:8080/jeecg-boot/energy/realtime/test/testGetParameters
Accept: application/json

### 3. 测试查询时序数据
GET http://localhost:8080/jeecg-boot/energy/realtime/test/testGetTimeSeriesData
Accept: application/json

### 4. 测试获取实时状态
GET http://localhost:8080/jeecg-boot/energy/realtime/test/testGetCurrentStatus
Accept: application/json

### 5. 正式接口 - 根据维度获取仪表列表
GET http://localhost:8080/jeecg-boot/energy/realtime/getModulesByDimension?dimensionCode=A02A02A01&energyType=1&includeChildren=true
Accept: application/json

### 6. 正式接口 - 获取参数配置
GET http://localhost:8080/jeecg-boot/energy/realtime/getParameterConfig?energyType=1
Accept: application/json

### 7. 正式接口 - 查询时序数据
POST http://localhost:8080/jeecg-boot/energy/realtime/getTimeSeriesData
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "moduleIds": ["yj0001_13", "yj0001_14"],
    "parameters": [1, 2, 7],
    "timeGranularity": "day",
    "queryDate": "2025-07-25"
}

### 8. 正式接口 - 获取实时状态
POST http://localhost:8080/jeecg-boot/energy/realtime/getCurrentStatus
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "moduleIds": ["yj0001_13", "yj0001_14"],
    "parameters": [1, 2, 7]
}

